hropathy.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/188335/', '', 'Enalapril, Moexipril, Ramipril, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Benazepril, Quinapril, Trandolapril, Captopril, Fosinopril, Tamsulosin, More', 'Ethiodized oil, Iopanoic acid, Tyropanoic acid, Iopodic acid', 1767369485);
